						 <p>I was thrown off by the 5000 number. Did you mean 500?</p> <p>Antarctica itself is roughly 5000km<sup>2</sup> isn't it? So &quot;re-directed to their basecamp&quot; doesn't seem to make sense if you did mean the whole continent.</p> 
