						 <p>Short, to the point, and odd in a good way. I really appreciate the clever details you added, such as the dates, including the recent economic downturn from coronavirus, or how the mountain is shaped like a graph of exponential growth. It’s short in length, but full in substance.</p> 
				 	]]>
